{"tid":821802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［力場不自保］紅磡海濱廣場失守 數十玻璃窗幾近盡毀滿目瘡痍　","createTime":"2018-09-16T05:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T05:16:32.000Z","uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73b76632ad1349feec1df9e3ae32ce51a77ee921","tid":821802,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180916/58687997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58687997&d=odiLod4TV3Vw2JosZDx6s0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=65fd3d5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58687997&h=746ed22d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180916/58687997</a><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」威力越接近中午越強勁，本港不少大廈的玻璃窗在颶風下不堪一擊，應聲破碎。其中紅磡海濱廣場二期有數十隻玻璃窗今早被狂風掃毀，滿目瘡痍，如戰場內的建築物，窗戶被毀單位內的大量雜物則被捲出大廈外，隨風盤旋飄舞如飛雪，情況既壯觀亦可怕。旁邊的九龍海逸君綽酒店，亦有窗戶被吹毀。<br />\n<br />\n另外，葵盛西龍順軒酒樓今早在風暴中照常營業，但窗戶無法抵受強風，整排窗被風吹跌，茶客狼狽走避。讀者韓先生當時正在酒樓內吃早點，突然聽到砰一聲，「成排窗冧咗落嚟」，韓先生即時躲在枱底，隨後見一地玻璃碎，「有幾個人靠窗邊，擦損咗，但冇叫白車」。酒樓事後亦關門暫停營業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537069251_014f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537069251_014f.jpg&h=be55efe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537069522_d7c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537069522_d7c9.jpg&h=a21f35c7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}